{"tid":2061744,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"(舊聞）【紅色球鞋】中資企斥資20億港元購K-Swiss母企，盼轉型全球公司！","createTime":"2020-06-12T15:15:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T01:16:53.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"266838329a2fe6fa8a7f97be7b0408d8ec1a0f70","tid":2061744,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:15:30.000Z","msg":"波鞋（球鞋）品牌K-swiss<br />\n已經被中國品牌 &ldquo;特步&rdquo;買走<br />\n請即刻拒買！<br />\nBy<br />\nCally<br />\non<br />\n03 May 2019<br />\nBusiness Reporter<br />\n<br />\n中國體育用品股特步（01368）昨日宣布，以現金2.6億美元（約20.4億港元），向國時裝及零售集團衣戀集團（E-Land），收購旗下E-Land Footwear USA的全部股份，該公司擁有美國運動鞋履品牌K-Swiss、法國軍靴品牌Palladium及Supra等品牌，預計今年7月底完成交易。特步股價昨偷步炒上，升4.5%。<br />\n<br />\nK-Swiss<br />\nPhoto from K-Swiss<br />\nK-Swiss、Palladium歷史悠久<br />\n<br />\nK-Swiss於1966年在美國創立，屹立至今已半個世紀，創辦人Brunner兄弟從瑞士移民南加州後愛上打網球，但卻發現大部份網球手並沒有一對適合及高機能的網球鞋，遂成立品牌。K代表製造商Kuenzli，SWISS則代表兩兄弟的家鄉。品牌後來推出全球第一對全皮網球鞋The Classic，奠定其網球鞋「一哥」地位。<br />\n<br />\nPalladium誕生於法國里昂，1920年做戰鬥機輪胎起家，直至1947年開始涉足軍靴領域，後來品牌加入一些流行新穎的元素，慢慢發展成今日的時尚品牌。<br />\n<br />\nPalladium<br />\nPhoto from Palladium<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n截至去年12月底K-Swiss及Palladium全年收益分別為1.09億美元及7790.7萬美元，按年升12%及9.65%。特步認為，K-Swiss及Palladium各自擁有獨特品牌定位及不同的目標客戶，與公司目前的品牌組合高度互補，有助公司轉型為全球體育用品公司。<br />\n<br />\n中資企業收購外國體育品牌絕非新鮮事，其中安踏（02020）早於2009年收購意大利運動休閒品牌FILA的中國業務；去年12月，由安踏牽頭的財團又再收購芬蘭運動品牌Amer Sports逾九成股權。"},{"pid":"0c9f2da9a30d06f30c50a55d5254f87a1bdb87a3","tid":2061744,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:16:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/NotChinaMade/permalink/3425615917472142/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2FNotChinaMade%2Fpermalink%2F3425615917472142%2F&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjDBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=27a62231\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/NotChinaMade/permalink/3425615917472142/</a>"},{"pid":"57792c1e1b5770afcda641587eff1107d8ea80b1","tid":2061744,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:24:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6625c79fc2342690fce5695f673e837417264dfe","tid":2061744,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T16:26:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ff5699106c0d947187aa2e7275bddcd084add88","tid":2061744,"uid":84409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T16:30:44.000Z","msg":"Bye <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然本身覺得樣衰都無人會買"},{"pid":"7d8b77f790d4bdbdae31da9e990ad9681afc730b","tid":2061744,"uid":235277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T16:32:00.000Z","msg":"乜原來仲有人買架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"560027dad3d139c8a6e49ac9271e76109025d0f9","tid":2061744,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7d8b77f790d4bdbdae31da9e990ad9681afc730b","tid":2061744,"uid":235277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T16:32:00.000Z","msg":"乜原來仲有人買架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T16:37:18.000Z","msg":"有人唔知買咗就幣，要提醒大家"},{"pid":"354b17cc808cfe42a6c716dfdde054b978f901df","tid":2061744,"uid":279357,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T18:59:46.000Z","msg":"大陸佬買呢間公司<br />\n唔係為咗整波鞋<br />\n亦都唔係要咗人哋個品牌<br />\n買咗呢間公司只係為走資<br />\n要搞佢只有美國查帳"},{"pid":"5981ecb1c993f2623541154dfca748e14ddf1634","tid":2061744,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T01:16:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}